{"tid":1034799,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"風險管理一問","createTime":"2019-02-24T07:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T08:22:43.000Z","uid":215833,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"69be7dbf23862c44be9922ab31d3d9c7199afe29","tid":1034799,"uid":215833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"有個問題困擾左我好耐,請教下各位。<br />\n風險個定義係uncertainty 即係不確定。咁既然定義上係uncertainty,點解d人仲要諗風險管理?如果可以量度到risk,咁仲算唔算係risk?"},{"pid":"1f682e58e9aee64bdcd35324a527a2fa2e67171f","tid":1034799,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"風險 有可控 及不可控"},{"pid":"923a2adf4c2d9e87f3fd9fab66b65442a486b126","tid":1034799,"uid":215833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f682e58e9aee64bdcd35324a527a2fa2e67171f","tid":1034799,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"風險 有可控 及不可控"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"你意思係systemic risk 同unsystemic risk?"},{"pid":"f3d32d1b2e1dc4e4100e228ce98ffefc3a228803","tid":1034799,"uid":64017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"量度到風險當然算係風險"},{"pid":"599ac77cd2707cb8392bc7e007c801f9fdb6c7eb","tid":1034799,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:47:16.000Z","msg":"因為有 uncertainty 所以有 expectation ，因為有 expectation 所以有 risk measure 。當然點樣用 stochastic process 去 model uncertainty 然後揾 expectation 係一門學問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bceffe3c23ef58628b0c05c20ff91c8885621530","tid":1034799,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"例如你唔知個天幾時落雨, 又唔鍾意睇天氣報告, 但係你驚比雨淋濕。<br />\n你可以選擇唔出街(avoid)或者隨時帶把遮出街, 等落雨果陣唔會淋到咁濕(reduce)。<br />\n依啲咪風險管理囉。"},{"pid":"0bef64a84f8e30c98ae634344e59fb96c807300e","tid":1034799,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"923a2adf4c2d9e87f3fd9f